				<td colspan="2"><span>I got the nostromo for my Ranger when I played her.  Turned out to be a nice tool for my bard as well.  I love it for twisting, targeting and being about to move around while doing it.
<br />

<br />
Can't recommend a profile.  I've set up my own, but I'm still tweaking it to get it right.  Have songs on the control pad (the one that look like '+' ) and movement similar to the WASD set up with various targeting option (previous, cycle, myself) around the movement keys.  Like I said I'm still tweaking it though.
<br />

<br />
Riveo Lindor - 65 bard on Torv</span></td>
