				<td colspan="2"><span>The N52 is a popular choice among bards. Use the search tool and look back at some semi-recent discussions about these, there have been a lot of them. The profiles are transferrable so we can share them but because they are so customizable, I really reccommend just playing around with it and finding something that intuitive for your play style. I don't know anyone that has one of these and doesn't love it, they're awesome, go back and look at some of the threads and then go buy one and check it out, you'll wonder why you didn't get one sooner. Upon second thought, you didn't say whether you had one or not...... 
